{"tid":761144,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人由小到大都極少病痛?","createTime":"2018-07-30T06:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T07:01:01.000Z","uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"863f717fdced114a990549a396016b6e07f667fc","tid":761144,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"利申︰我係<br />\n小學到中學平均兩年先一日病假(多數係扮病唔想返)<br />\n青春期剩用清水洗臉無爆過暗瘡<br />\n<br />\n個鼻一年365日都唔會塞, 一個星期都做唔到一次運動<br />\n十幾年未試過肚痾/嘔/發燒<br />\n只係試過有排壓力大會偏頭痛<br />\n<br />\n身邊啲朋友話發燒但已經唔記得係咩感受<br />\n有時會覺得咁早做哂啲健康quota會好早死, 有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb31b76d793fc99c1bae778b4cb72d818f7ebe5","tid":761144,"uid":82698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:59:22.000Z","msg":"一係唔病 一病就。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a17b281e998a1695c8dfaeb2dcf2b91ab9fad5","tid":761144,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb31b76d793fc99c1bae778b4cb72d818f7ebe5","tid":761144,"uid":82698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:59:22.000Z","msg":"一係唔病 一病就。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"好嚴重, 好唔好得返果隻?"},{"pid":"d265a6c3f74da6046c09059664a64a136a8fad1f","tid":761144,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}